"title": "5961: superiority",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5961: superiority",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sense of being of greater importance or value in comparison with others, which can lead to arrogance and boasting.</p>\n<h2>Superiority is a characteristic of the wicked person</h2>\n<h3>It is the product of human pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:24\">PRO 21:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:9\">3JN 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16\">2CH 26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:3-Ps73:9\">PSA 73:3–73:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:16\">ISA 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:9-Isa9:10\">ISA 9:9–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:30\">ROM 1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:4\">2TI 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">2PE 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>It involves looking down on others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:42\">1SA 17:42</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:4-Gen16:5\">GEN 16:4–16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:27\">1SA 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:16\">2SA 6:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:29\">1CH 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:18\">PSA 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:5\">PSA 101:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps123:3-Ps123:4\">PSA 123:3–123:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:20\">PRO 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:10\">AMO 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>It gives rise to boasting</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:11\">EST 5:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9\">ACT 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:11\">1KI 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:6\">ISA 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:2\">EZK 28:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:8\">DAN 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:8\">HOS 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:33-Matt26:35\">MAT 26:33–26:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:5\">JAS 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:16\">JUD 1:16</a></p>\n<h2>God hates superior behaviour and will judge it</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:11-Isa2:12\">ISA 2:11–2:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:3\">1SA 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:28\">2SA 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:6-Job20:7\">JOB 20:6–20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11\">PRO 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:5\">PRO 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:18\">PRO 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:4\">PRO 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:17\">ISA 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:12\">ISA 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:19\">ISA 13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:9\">ISA 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:12-Obad1:13\">OBA 1:12–1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:10\">MAT 18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17-Rom11:18\">ROM 11:17–11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:3\">ROM 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:10\">ROM 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:20-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:20–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">1TI 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:7-Rev18:8\">REV 18:7–18:8</a></p>\n<h2>The attitude of the godly is not superior</h2>\n<h3>They demonstrate a proper humility</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps131:1\">PSA 131:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3\">PHP 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:6-1Cor4:7\">1CO 4:6–4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:4-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:4–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's advice to those who aspire to greatness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:20-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:20–20:28</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:35-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:35–10:45</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:12-John13:17\">JHN 13:12–13:17</a></p>",
